Sweet Potato Waffles (gf)

1 sweet potato (~1.5 c) peeled and grated
1 large egg
2 tbsp coconut flour
1/2 tsp salt

Preheat waffle iron. In a large bowl, combine all ingredients. Spray iron generously with nonstick spray. Spoon 1/2 batter into center of iron; close lid and cook for 5-8 min, or until golden brown. Remove and repeat with second half of batter.

